lass=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.9386em;vertical-align:-0.2441em;\"></span><span class=\"mop\"><span class=\"mop\">lo<span style=\"margin-right:0.01389em;\">g</span></span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.207em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.4559em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2441em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.10903em;\">N</span></span></span></span>","key":"H4FVyfpXBW"}],"key":"cs40MOGFvP"}],"key":"cyfJLngOzR"},{"type":"block","kind":"notebook-content","children":[{"type":"image","url":"/notes/build/807df35ea85c467048e2d627c4b2bbfd.png","width":500,"key":"bEMkODVBUh","urlSource":"data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGg...VORK5CYII="}],"key":"gCW5eHL2d6"},{"type":"block","kind":"notebook-code","children":[{"type":"code","lang":"python","executable":true,"value":"def binary_search(arr: list[int], target: int) -> int:\n    \"\"\"二分探索でarrにおけるtargetのindexを返す\n    \n    arr: list[int]\n        ソート済みのlist\n    \"\"\"\n    # 探索範囲の左端のインデックス\n    left = 0\n    # 探索範囲の右端のインデックス\n    right = len(arr) - 1\n\n    # left が right を超えるまで探索を続ける\n    # left <= right の間は、まだ探索範囲が残っている\n    while left <= right:\n        # 探索範囲の中央のインデックスを求める\n        mid = (left + right) // 2\n\n        # 中央の値が target と一致したら、その位置を返す\n        if arr[mid] == target:\n            return mid  # targetのindex\n\n        # 中央の値が target より小さい場合\n        elif arr[mid] < target:\n            # target は中央より右側にあるはずなので、探索範囲の左端を mid + 1 にずらす\n            left = mid + 1\n\n        # 中央の値が target より大きい場合\n        else:\n            # target は中央より左側にあるはずなので、範囲の右端を mid - 1 にずらす\n            right = mid - 1\n\n    # 探索範囲がなくなっても見つからなかった（arrにtargetが含まれない）場合\n    return -1","key":"GK8GDcfrOr"},{"type":"outputs","id":"ML41R8gGake934Zbl8JuV","children":[],"key":"jbXGd5hf3H"}],"key":"XTEsBgMmHb"},{"type":"block","kind":"notebook-code","children":[{"type":"code","lang":"python","executable":true,"value":"numbers = [1, 3, 5, 7, 9, 11, 13]\nbinary_search(numbers, 7)","key":"DRY9JbczpT"},{"type":"outputs","id":"gS1ft1GTy6I__xu6gpsxV","children":[{"type":"output","jupyter_data":{"output_type":"execute_result","execution_count":11,"metadata":{},"data":{"text/plain":{"content":"7","content_type":"text/plain"}}},"children":[],"key":"fanl9aTUDx"}],"key":"Dd6rxRLO67"}],"key":"t7AnXW02ck"},{"type":"block","kind":"notebook-content","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1},"end":{"line":1,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"関連：bisectパッケージ","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1},"end":{"line":1,"column":1}},"key":"eyWUeYDI1O"}],"identifier":"id-bisect","label":"関連：bisectパッケージ","html_id":"id-bisect","implicit":true,"key":"mNhMs4cFQT"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Pythonの標準パッケージ ","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"evpgCK6Xr0"},{"type":"inlineCode","value":"bisect","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"S5xJQ8LwOR"},{"type":"text","value":" は二分探索で実装されている","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"Dbt0zznVxm"}],"key":"xiBAst17wi"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"link","url":"https://docs.python.org/ja/3/library/bisect.html","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"typ